title: BLUE: Vol 1 (Seeking Blue Charity Mix)
tags: ['charity', 'mitis', 'ninajirachi', 'SheepyPlaylistAll', 'suicide prevention', 'echos', 'MrSuicideSheep', 'Music', 'charity stream', 'seeking blue records', 'to write love on her arms', 'dabin', 'twloha', 'xan griffin', 'mrsuicidesheep charity stream', 'seeking blue', 'said the sky', 'suicide sheep', 'ihf', 'sheepy', 'illenium']
description:
All proceeds from this video will go to To Write Love On Her Arms!

We raised a total of $17,740 for TWLOHA in the 12 hour Livestream! JUST AMAZING!!! Words can't express how wonderful that was to be part of. I'm proud of you. #RaisetheGoal

Spotify playlist of the whole 12 hours! http://sptfy.com/16bG

Compilation coming on Friday!

Tracklist:
0:00 MitiS - ‘Til The End
3:37 - Said the Sky & Kwesi - All I Got
8:17 - Yoe Mase - Despite All
12:53 - Xan Griffin - Gemini (feat. WILD)
17:16 - Hazey Eyes - Need You
19:49 - Illenium - No Time Like Now
21:47 - Dabin - In Flames (feat. Lexi Norton)
25:07 - Finding Hope - 3:00AM
28:20 - Illenium - Beautiful Creatures (Julian Marchal Rework)
30:25 - JANEE - What Are You Doing Here (feat. Casey Breves)
34:08 - Said The Sky x FRND - Faded
37:28 - Ninajirachi - Pure Luck
40:34 - Other - Safety (feat. Brandon banks)
43:43 - IHF - Awake
47:01 - Echos - Haunt

The SEEKING BLUE Logo artwork was created by Manuel Martin https://www.behance.net/ManuelMartinDucharne

title: gnash - i hate u i love u (feat. olivia o'brien) (lyrics)
tags: ['I hate you I love you', 'Indie Pop', 'SheepyPlaylistAll', 'gnash I hate you I love you', 'gnash', 'Pop', 'MrSuicideSheep', 'Electronic Pop', 'gnash I hate u I love u', 'Chill R&B', 'Electronic R&B']
description:
gnash - i hate u i love u (feat. olivia o'brien) (lyrics)

⬙  FAVOURITES ON SPOTIFY ⬙
⇥ http://mrsuicidesheep.com/favourites 

I hate you I love you... gnash's track 'i hate u i love u' with olivia o'brien is one of the best things I've heard this year!
Watch the official music video...http://bit.ly/1Ry9dxd
Download... http://bit.ly/1R3ga4Y
Stream on Spotify...http://spoti.fi/1VBTQDJ

Lyrics

Feeling used
But I'm
Still missing you
And I can't
See the end of this
Just wanna feel your kiss
Against my lips
And now all this time
Is passing by
But I still can't seem to tell you why
It hurts me every time I see you
Realize how much I need you

I hate you I love you
I hate that I love you
Don't want to, but I can't put
Nobody else above you
I hate you I love you
I hate that I want you
You want her, you need her
And I'll never be her

I miss you when I can't sleep
Or right after coffee
Or right when I can't eat
I miss you in my front seat
Still got sand in my sweaters
From nights we don't remember
Do you miss me like I miss you?
Fucked around and got attached to you
Friends can break your heart too, and
I'm always tired but never of you
If I pulled a you on you, you wouldn't like that shit
I put this reel out, but you wouldn't bite that shit
I type a text but then I nevermind that shit
I got these feelings but you never mind that shit
Oh oh, keep it on the low
You're still in love with me but your friends don't know
If u wanted me you would just say so
And if I were you, I would never let me go
I don't mean no harm
I just miss you on my arm
Wedding bells were just alarms
Caution tape around my heart
You ever wonder what we could have been?
You said you wouldn't and you fucking did
Lie to me, lie with me, get your fucking fix
Now all my drinks and all my feelings are all fucking mixed
Always missing people that I shouldn't be missing
Sometimes you gotta burn some bridges just to create some distance
I know that I control my thoughts and I should stop reminiscing
But I learned from my dad that it's good to have feelings
When love and trust are gone
I guess this is moving on
Everyone I do right does me wrong
So every lonely night, I sing this song

I hate you I love you
I hate that I love you
Don't want to, but I can't put
Nobody else above you
I hate you I love you
I hate that I want you
You want her, you need her
And I'll never be her

All alone I watch you watch her
Like she's the only girl you've ever seen
You don't care you never did
You don't give a damn about me
Yeah all alone I watch you watch her
She's the only thing you've ever seen
How is it you never notice
That you are slowly killing me

I hate you I love you
I hate that I love you
Don't want to, but I can't put
Nobody else above you
I hate you I love you
I hate that I want you
You want her, you need her
And I'll never be her

title: Taking You Deeper (Deep House Mix)
tags: ['Monarch', 'Vice', 'Kraak & Smaak', 'House Music Mix', 'Deep House Mix 2015', 'Deepend', "N'to", 'Elderbrook', 'Tez Cadey', 'Ansah', 'SheepyPlaylistAll', 'Listenbee', 'Deep House (Musical Genre)', 'Deep House 2015', 'Tube & Berger (Musical Artist)', 'MrSuicideSheep', 'Embody', 'Worakls', 'Maceo Plex', 'Best Deep House Mix', 'Vocal House (Musical Genre)', 'Music', 'Deep House Music', 'House Music (Musical Genre)', 'Touch & Go', 'Pedestrian', 'Anthony Hamilton (Musical Artist)', 'Jason Burns', 'Wild Culture']
description:
Taking You Deeper (Deep House Mix)

⬙  FAVOURITES ON SPOTIFY ⬙
⇥ http://mrsuicidesheep.com/favourites

First deep house mix!

"This mix represents the greatest adventure in life.

We all begin in the same place: open, excited, and slightly uncertain. The road is filled with possibilities compelling us to move forward. Eventually, we latch onto a comforting groove by finding pieces of what we call home.

Then, it all changes. The turbulence, the chaos, the depths we need to experience to find what is truly on the other side. No home can be complete without this one thing, and any true story is lacking in its absence…

The greatest discovery on any journey is love."

Download for free... http://bit.ly/1L6SOKI

author: MrSuicideSheep
title: 'Dawn' Pt. 2 (An Ambient Mix)
tags: ['Catching Flies', 'Ambient Mix', 'Downtempo (Musical Genre)', 'Owsey', 'Chill Out Mix', 'Tom Day', 'Chill Out Music', 'MrSuicideSheep', 'Dominick Martin', 'The Flashbulb', 'Dawn Pt. An Ambient Mix', 'Ambient Music (Broadcast Genre)', 'Helios', 'Koda', 'Rhian Sheehan (Musical Artist)', 'Hiatus', 'SheepyPlaylistAll', 'Sorrow']
description:
Hey everyone, after exactly 2 years I've finally managed to bring you the next instalment of the ambient mix. I really hope you guys enjoy it!  This mix is supposed to capture the feeling of sitting on the edge of a mountain and watching the sun rise over the horizon. It's about letting go of your past and looking ahead to new beginnings.

Mixed by the very talented Aeuria. Make sure to check him out and give him your support.
https://soundcloud.com/aeuria
https://twitter.com/aeuria
https://www.facebook.com/Aeuria

author: MrSuicideSheep
title: 'Taking You Higher Pt. 3' (Progressive House Mix)
tags: ['Taking You Higher Progressive House Mix 3', 'Boom Jinx & Soundprank', 'Michael Brun', 'Mango', 'MrSuicideSheep Taking You Higher', 'Dirty South (Composer)', 'George Acosta', 'Taking You Higher', 'MrSuicideSheep', 'Cosmic Gate (Musical Artist)', 'LTN', 'Johan Vilborg', 'Hazem Beltagui', 'Blood Groove & Kikis', 'Matt Lange', 'Taking You Higher 3', 'Dan & Sam', 'Claes Rosen', 'Jethimself', 'Juventa', 'Solarity', 'Teen Daze', 'Andrew Bayer', 'Taking You Higher Part 3', 'SheepyPlaylistAll', 'Nigel Good']
description:
'Taking You Higher Pt. 3' (Progressive House Mix)

⬙  FAVOURITES ON SPOTIFY ⬙
⇥ http://mrsuicidesheep.com/favourites

The new 'Taking You Higher' is finally here! Any support is truly appreciated. 
Download on iTunes... http://bit.ly/YJBeIg
Listen on Spotify... http://spoti.fi/1Cazg2Y

Hey everyone :) As a lot of you are aware, the 'Taking You Higher' series has been a big part of this channel for the past 3 years. The feelings I want to convey with these mixes are of euphoria and elation. It's about letting go of all your worries, following your dreams and truly taking you to a higher place. This is the first mix in the series that I have decided to release as a compilation. If you would like to support the artists and labels (as well as the series in general) that have been a part of making this possible, please consider supporting by either downloading it on iTunes or streaming it through Spotify, Google Play, Deezer or any other site. 

Mixed by the very talented Aaron Static
https://soundcloud.com/aaronstatic
https://www.facebook.com/aaronstatic

Tracklist
00:00 Gregory Esayan - Innerspace (Dan & Sam Intro Mix)
08:38 Juventa - Move Into Light (feat. Erica Curran) (Teen Daze Remix)
11:39 Simon J - Life Thru A Lens (Inners Remix)
17:23 Soulforge - Dreamfast
23:07 Nafis - Summer Feeling (Redubs At 5AM Remix)
28:33 George Acosta - Beautiful (feat. Fisher)
32:55 Gal Abutbul - Sunset
38:08 Helvetic Nerds - Stormwatch (Chris Reece & Dinka Old Fashion Mix)
45:39 Valer den Bit - Meteor 15 (ArcHouse Remix)
52:38 Aeron Aether, Mango & Andre Frauenstein - Disappear (feat. Stefan Ludik)
55:51 Nigel Good - Come Home (LTN Remix)
59:09 Edu - Action Hero
01:04:08 Jacob Henry - Hopeful Romantic (Johan Vilborg Remix)
01:10:38 Dirty South - Your Heart (feat. Joel Gil) (Michael Brun Remix)
01:14:59 Boomjinx & Soundprank - Pieces Of A Puzzle (Solarity Remix)
01:21:15 Hazem Beltagui - She Came
01:27:15 Vintage & Morelli - For You
01:33:30 Our Stolen Theory - Warmest Day (Nigel Good Remix)
01:39:23 Cosmic Gate & Andrew Bayer - Nothing Ever Lasts (Extended Intro Mix)
01:45:39 Matt Lange - Sixty Six
01:51:37 Claes Rosen - Starlight (Blood Groove & Kikis Remix)
01:56:25 Jethimself - Canopy

tags: ['Jonas Mantey', 'George Acosta', 'Taking You Higher Part 2', 'Melodic', 'Trance Mix', 'Lessov', 'Taking You Higher', 'MrSuicideSheep', 'House Mix', 'Adam K & Soha', 'Nitrous Oxide', 'Deadmau5', 'SheepyPlaylistAll', 'Best Mix 2013', 'Ben Preston', 'Tiesto', 'Chicane', 'Johan Vilborg', 'Shingo Nakamura', 'Trance', 'Summer', 'Dinka', 'T.O.M', 'Arty', 'Progressive House Mix', 'Matteo Marini', 'Mix 2013', 'Youandewan', 'Soundprank', 'Progressive House', 'Electronic', 'Bass', 'Progressive Mix', 'Driving', 'Mango', 'Uplifting']
description:
'Taking You Higher Pt. 2' (Progressive House Mix)

⬙  FAVOURITES ON SPOTIFY ⬙
⇥ http://mrsuicidesheep.com/favourites

'Taking You Higher' Pt. 3
Support here... http://bit.ly/YJBeIg

So a year after 'Taking You Higher' Rameses B and I decided to put out another summery progressive house mix. This is perfect for road trips, late night chats, barbecues and just about any situation in life. Enjoy :)
I also got a new t-shirt made to go along with the release of this mix!
http://bit.ly/Sheepytees

A big thank you to all the artists featured in this mix and to Rameses B for mixing it.
https://soundcloud.com/ramesesb
https://www.facebook.com/RamesesB.off...
https://twitter.com/ramesesb
http://www.youtube.com/ramesesb

02:41 Dinka - Elements (EDX's 5un5hine Remix)

description:
'Dawn' An Ambient Mix

⬙  FAVOURITES ON SPOTIFY ⬙
⇥ http://mrsuicidesheep.com/favourites 

Sometimes you realize there are more important things in life. This is the perfect mix for you to lay under the stars and gaze up in awe.
Until dawn... to new beginnings.

Tracks chosen by myself and mixed by Sorrow. Give him your love!
http://soundcloud.com/sorrowgarage
http://www.facebook.com/sorrowgarage
https://twitter.com/sorrowgarage

description:
'Infinite Elation' (Progressive House Mix)

⬙  FAVOURITES ON SPOTIFY ⬙
⇥ http://mrsuicidesheep.com/favourites 

This one tries to bring out the same emotions as 'Taking You Higher', using incredibly melodic and warm, as well as nostalgia evoking, tracks. Hope you guys enjoy it as much as I do.
Tracks were chosen by myself and mixed by Aaron Static. He did an unbelievably good job on the mixing, letting the songs flow together seamlessly. Give him your love.
http://www.facebook.com/aaronstatic
http://soundcloud.com/aaronstatic
